 an uncompromising focus on materiality. Today, 02A Studio architects Marco Rulli and Thomas Grossi reinterpret these features, infusing them with the lively palette and whimsical forms of pop art. The result is a home that dances between the stark and the playful, the rigid and the fluid.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560991\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560991\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-3-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A person is cooking in a colorful kitchen with plants and modern decor, including a green dining table, pink chairs, and a tall white sculpture.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-3-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-3-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-3.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560992\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560992\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-4-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with striped walls, colorful art toys, a green swivel chair, and built-in shelves with books and plants.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-4-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-4-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-4-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-4-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAccording to Rulli, the aim was to “celebrate the home’s rich heritage while infusing it with the quirky, joyful aesthetic of its new owners, actress \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/martinapinto/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eMartina Pinto\u003c/a\u003e and director \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/alessandro_poggi/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eAlessandro Poggi\u003c/a\u003e.” The project preserves the apartment’s robust character, yet softens its edges, creating an environment that is as functional as it is expressive.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560993\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560993\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-5-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"Room with striped wall, large figurines on display shelves, books, a green chair with a colorful cushion, and a small plant.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-5-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-5-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-5-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-5-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-5.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560994\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560994\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"