-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560998\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560998\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-10-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"A kitchen with yellow cabinets, white tiled walls, a black chalkboard, and shelves holding décor and plants. A concrete pillar with an exposed edge is visible on the left.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-10-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-10-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-10-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-10-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=560999\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-560999\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-11-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"A person walking in a modern kitchen with tiled counters, a sink, shelves with various items, potted plants, and a natural wood partition.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-11-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-11-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-11-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-11-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561000\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561000\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-12-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"A hallway with wide horizontal striped walls features a large black sculptural figure standing in the center. A plant is on the left, and shelves with books are on the right.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-12-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-12-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-12-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-12-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEach room introduces a new layer of personality. In the hallway, lilac stripes cloak hidden storage, transforming utility into art. Meanwhile, the primary bedroom embraces a cartoonish charm, with flowing lines, plush furnishings, and a dreamy light blue carpet. The ensuite bathroom further explores this theme, where pastel tones and undulating forms meet sleek, industrial partitions. “This project embodies a perfect fusion of two worlds,” says Marco Rulli, co-founder of the studio with Thomas Grossi. “I love homes with a story to tell, and this one – with its layered patterns and eccentric furnishings – brings together different identities in a way that feels both unexpected and harmonious.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561001\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561001\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-13-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A bedroom features a white bed, a translucent side table with a lamp, a pink-framed mirror, orange curtains, and a wall with a purple and peach geometric pattern.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-13-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-13-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-13-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561002\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561002\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-14-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"A bedroom with a bed, ruffled white bedding, pastel wavy-patterned wallpaper, and a round side table holding a small green-striped lamp and a pink cup.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-14-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-14-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-14-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-14-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561003\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561003\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-15-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A bedroom with a white bed, pink and yellow patterned accent wall, gold curtain, and eclectic wall art. A small pink mirror and lamp are beside the bed.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-15-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-15-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-15-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561004\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561004\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-16-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"A view through a wavy green doorway shows a room with pastel pink tiles, a circular mirror, and a purple lamp. A framed picture hangs on the left wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-16-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-16-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-16-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-16-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561005\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561005\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-17-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"View of a colorful bathroom with a green scalloped doorway. Features a pink vanity, round mirror, and purple pendant light. Walls and floor are light-colored with pink curtain accents.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-17-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-17-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-17-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-17-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe bathroom’s doorway is framed with a light green wavy border that leads into the light pink tiled space. A matching pink fluted vanity with a countertop wrapped in the same green as the doorway becomes the focal point seen from the bedroom. A contrasting pale yellow mirror introduces an unexpected new color that’s a welcome addition.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561006\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561006\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-18-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"Colorful bathroom with a round mirror, pastel pink striped vanity, vessel sink, and green and pink decor elements.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-18-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-18-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-18-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-18-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561007\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561007\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-19-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Pastel-themed bathroom with a round mirror, a white vessel sink, and a pink-striped vanity. Green and pink curtains frame the space.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-19-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-19-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-19-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561008\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561008\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-20-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Room with a pastel color scheme, featuring a bed, a patterned accent wall, and a bathroom with pink tiles and a colorful shower curtain.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-20-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-20-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-20-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561009\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561009\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-21-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"Shower with a pink tiled wall and a green and pink checkered shower curtain featuring floral patterns.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-21-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-21-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-21-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-21-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561010\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561010\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-22-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A bathroom with pink tiles, a shower with a floral curtain, and a toilet and bidet. A green frame separates the shower area, and a shelf with decor is above the toilet.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-22-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-22-800x534.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-22-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-22.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThough visually striking, Casa Polly is designed with family life at its core. The reconfiguration includes a child’s bedroom, a walk-in closet, and a dedicated laundry area – all integrated into the home’s playful aesthetic. Every corner of the apartment speaks to a careful balance between form and function, ensuring it remains both practical and delightful.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561011\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561011\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-23-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"A pastel-themed children\u0026#39;s room with a floor bed, soft toys, a colorful dresser, and wall shelves holding books and decor items. A pink rug with green patterns lies on the floor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-23-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-23-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-23-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-23-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-23.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAt the heart of Casa Polly’s transformation lies 02A Studio’s commitment to crafting homes that resonate deeply with their inhabitants. Founded a decade ago, the studio approaches each project as an intricate puzzle, where client aspirations, architectural constraints, and artistic vision converge. For Rulli and Grossi, architecture is more than the sum of its parts; it’s a medium for storytelling and a means to foster joy.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=561012\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-561012\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-24-810x1276.jpg\" alt=\"A minimalist bathroom with a walk-in shower, black and white grid tiles, a white shower curtain, a round basin on a tiled countertop, a wall mirror, and a purple robe hanging on the wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1276\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-24-810x1276.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-24-800x1260.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-24-768x1210.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-24-975x1536.jpg 975w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/10/Casa-Polly-Rome-02A-Studio-24.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more information on 02A Studio, visit \u003ca href=\"https://www.02a.it/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eo2a.it\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ePhotography by Giulia Natalia Comito.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eCaroline Williamson is Editor-in-Chief of Design Milk. She has a BFA in photography from SCAD and can usually be found searching for vintage wares, doing New York Times crossword puzzles in pen, or reworking playlists on Spotify.\u003c/p\u003e\n                                    \n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n                            \u003c/div\u003e\n                                            \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
